  "needToEndorseCount": 0,
  "outcome": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　　降低民眾取得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L.5400</span><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">醫療器材的門檻，得以增加其他廠商進口</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L.5400</span><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">的意願，讓有心耕耘的廠商能依法申請藥商執照，取得醫療器材許可證，合法販售月事用品，以保障民眾的使用安全，擴充台灣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L.5400</span><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">品項的選擇多樣性，同時利於經期教育和推廣。</span></span></p>",
  "outline": "月事用品在台灣的販售推廣向來有諸多限制，因被歐盟歸類為民生用品的衛生棉條（tampon）和月經量杯（menstrualcup），在台灣官方分類卻隸屬二級醫療器材，實務上需要執照及檢驗程序，個人進口則需要診斷證明書，導致衛生棉條選擇較少，而月經量杯尚未發給執照，法規的限制使得相關執照申請手續繁瑣，導致少有廠商願意生產、進口或代理。月經量杯（menstrualcup）俗稱「月亮杯」，是用醫療級矽膠材質",
